title: Starman
description: An alien stranded on Earth clones himself into the form of a young woman's deceased husband, kidnapping her as he attempts to reunite with his spacecraft to make his way home. (1984)
description2: An alien stranded on Earth clones himself into the form of a young woman's deceased husband, kidnapping her as he attempts to reunite with his spacecraft to make his way home.

title: Infamous
description: Intrigued by a murder in Kansas, writer Truman Capote begins researching for his new novel and develops an intense relationship with the convicted killer that could pose devastating emotional consequences. (2006)
description2: Intrigued by a murder in Kansas, writer Truman Capote begins researching for his new novel and develops an intense relationship with the convicted killer that could pose devastating emotional consequences.

title: Tickled
description: Journalist David Farrier stumbles upon a mysterious tickling competition online. As he delves deeper he comes up against fierce resistance, but that doesn't stop him getting to the bottom of a story stranger than fiction. (2016)
description2: Journalist David Farrier stumbles upon a mysterious tickling competition online. As he delves deeper he comes up against fierce resistance, but that doesn't stop him getting to the bottom of a story stranger than fiction.

title: Absolutely Anything
description: Aliens place the fate of humanity in the hands of a schoolteacher, bestowing him the ability to do absolutely anything, but only his talking dog seems to have any idea how to use the power properly. (2013)
description2: Aliens place the fate of humanity in the hands of a schoolteacher, bestowing him the ability to do absolutely anything, but only his talking dog seems to have any idea how to use the power properly.

episode_title: Play School: The Very Silly Special
title: Play School: The Very Silly Special
episode_name: Play School: The Very Silly Special
description: Join Michelle, Leah, Matt, Alex and Emma, plus a live 4-piece band as they bring us your favourite Play School songs and the silliest shenanigans in this celebration of silliness and laughter.
description2: Join Michelle, Leah, Matt, Alex and Emma, plus a live 4-piece band as they bring us your favourite Play School songs and the silliest shenanigans in this celebration of silliness and laughter.

title: The Larkins At Christmas
description: The Larkins are preparing for Christmas, but there's been burglaries in the village. Pop and Ma are overjoyed to have Mariette and Charley back for Christmas, but when Charley's parents arrive chaos descends on the farm.
